160.8	Turmeric	Turmeric	Turmeric is a rhizomatous herbaceous perennial plant of the ginger family, Zingiberaceae. It is native to tropical South Asia and needs temperatures between 20 째C and 30 째C (68 째F and 86 째F) and a considerable amount of annual rainfall to thrive. Plants are gathered annually for their rhizomes, and propagated from some of those rhizomes in the following season.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Curcuma_longa_%28Haldi%29_W_IMG_2440.jpg/220px-Curcuma_longa_%28Haldi%29_W_IMG_2440.jpg
